__e: Doctor... We don't seek to rule this world.
Since it is the destiny of the British and Americans to rule the world... the better we know each other... the better we will do it.
Give them the greatest gifts of all... powers beyond imagination... and they may think they're meant to rule the world.
Since it is the destiny of the British and Americans to rule the world... the better we know each other... the better we will do it.
*And I know one day will never reign supreme.*
And as long as I must dwell in hell, I might as well rule it.
But how long will it be before these gods decide to rule instead of serve?
Twenty thousand years ago, Grandpa Lucifer said... "It's better to rule in Hell than to serve in Heaven."
